# Un-ignore only the committed Tool Guide policy files for this example.
# The root .gitignore has a bare `.cuga` rule intended for runtime folders;
# these overrides ensure the example's policy files are tracked by git.
!.cuga/
!.cuga/tool_guides/
!.cuga/tool_guides/policy_employee.md
!.cuga/tool_guides/policy_manager.md
!.cuga/tool_guides/policy_executive.md
